{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had such terrible problems, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't keep food down and-- and yet, I couldn't refuse food, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a real dilemma.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I arrived in this town of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now this-- we were Slovakia again, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is the way things change, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like after the war, where I was in Hungary, our town became Czechoslovakia again, because the Hungarians lost the war and so Czechoslovakia became a country again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We took back-- they took back all the lost areas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I came to [INAUDIBLE], and I went to the place where there's a market and the farmers come in from all the neighboring towns.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I thought that maybe I can find a farmer from my town and hitch a ride back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I went there, and I was looking for a face that I would recognize, and I recognized a farmer from my town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I told him who I was, and he didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't know who I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just didn't look like this person, you know, like I did a year ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I asked him whether he can give me a lift back home, and he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
